             were indicted for <rs id="t18051204-20-off120" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18051204-20-off120" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18051204-20-off120" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18051204-20-cd121" type="crimeDate">20th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18051204-20-off120 t18051204-20-cd121"></join>, one sheet value 2 s. 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18051204-20-victim235" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Riggs
                        <interp inst="t18051204-20-victim235" type="surname" value="Riggs"></interp>
