                  </persName>
             sworn. - I produce three shirts, and four handkerchiefs; they were brought to me on Wednesday evening, the 20th of Nov. by the senior prisoner, between six and seven o'clock, he asked me twenty-five shillings for these articles; he said they were his wife's brother, he had sent him with them, and they were marked with the initials of 
               <persName id="t18051204-20-person256">
                  Thomas 
                  Reid
               <interp inst="t18051204-20-person256" type="surname" value="Reid"></interp>
