                  </persName>
            , the person, he said they belonged to; I advanced him seventeen shillings and sixpence on them; they have been in my custody ever since. (The property identified by Mr. Riggs the elder. and the younger, and 
               <persName id="t18051204-20-person257">
                  Ann 
                  Eastess
               <interp inst="t18051204-20-person257" type="surname" value="Eastess"></interp>
